        <div class="msgSubject">MUST haves for a tank.</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-17 18:55:53   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1290041753247502267" id="quote-1290041753247502267" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1290041753247502267" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=175&amp;mid=1290041753247502267&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1290041753247502267&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1290041753247502267" onclick="followToggle('add','1290041753247502267')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
