      <div class="msgContentFrame">Just thought id write a post on what are the essentials for anyone wanting to tank. Before you even think about tanking for a party you should have these skills  <br /> <br />************************************************************************************************************************ <br />TAUNT - Rank 10 Pugilist skill - Absolute essential for hate control <br /> <br />DEFENDER - Rank 10 Marauder skill - A buff that gives you more defence and makes you gain more hate in steadfast stance, cant go wrong with that. <br />************************************************************************************************************************ <br /> <br />CURE - Rank 10 Conjurer skill - Not essential but I found it pretty handy early when I was in a party with no healer, your job is just to get the mobs attention and keep yourself alive (you've also got Second Wind from having pugilist rank 10) <br /> <br />I know this stuff is pretty basic and everyone should have them but I ran into a rank 19 Gladiator tonight who didn't have any of these so I thought I'd write this for those people and obviously for people who are new to the game.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4454266" title="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4454266" rel="external nofollow">http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4454266</a> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1812910.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
